metadata.Plot: Grace, an aspiring model, is thrilled to have fashion photographer Hunter Kelly help launch her career. But when the photo shoot becomes a kidnapping showing Hunter's true intentions to use Grace as his next "star" on a sexy website, Grace must find a way to escape before she becomes Hunter's next model murder victim.
